ne":31,"column":6,"nodeType":"462","endLine":31,"endColumn":8,"suggestions":"541"},"react-hooks/exhaustive-deps","Effect callbacks are synchronous to prevent race conditions. Put the async function inside:\n\nuseEffect(() => {\n  async function fetchData() {\n    // You can await here\n    const response = await MyAPI.getData(someId);\n    // ...\n  }\n  fetchData();\n}, [someId]); // Or [] if effect doesn't need props or state\n\nLearn more about data fetching with Hooks: https://reactjs.org/link/hooks-data-fetching","ArrowFunctionExpression","React Hook useEffect has missing dependencies: 'dispatch' and 'socket'. Either include them or remove the dependency array.","ArrayExpression",["542"],"React Hook useEffect has a missing dependency: 'actionGetMenu'. Either include it or remove the dependency array.",["543"],"React Hook useEffect has a missing dependency: 'dispatch'. Either include it or remove the dependency array.",["544"],"React Hook useEffect has missing dependencies: 'dataProductsId', 'dispatch', and 'historyProduct'. Either include them or remove the dependency array.",["545"],"React Hook useEffect has missing dependencies: 'dispatch' and 'name_Trademark'. Either include them or remove the dependency array.",["546"],"React Hook useEffect has missing dependencies: 'form' and 'history'. Either include them or remove the dependency array.",["547"],"React Hook useEffect has missing dependencies: 'dispatch' and 'paramsType'. Either include them or remove the dependency array.",["548"],["549"],"React Hook useEffect has missing dependencies: 'dispatch' and 'params'. Either include them or remove the dependency array.",["550"],["551"],"React Hook useEffect has a missing dependency: 'getDataComments'. Either include it or remove the dependency array.",["552"],"React Hook useEffect has missing dependencies: 'form', 'history', and 'patchCart'. Either include them or remove the dependency array. Outer scope values like 'tokenLocal' aren't valid dependencies because mutating them doesn't re-render the component.",["553"],"React Hook useEffect has a missing dependency: 'setPatchCart'. Either include it or remove the dependency array. If 'setPatchCart' changes too often, find the parent component that defines it and wrap that definition in useCallback.",["554"],"React Hook useEffect has missing dependencies: 'actionGetProductAll', 'actionGetProductSlider', and 'actionGetProductType'. Either include them or remove the dependency array.",["555"],"jsx-a11y/anchor-is-valid","The href attribute is required for an anchor to be keyboard accessible. Provide a valid, navigable address as the href value. If you cannot provide an href, but still need the element to resemble a link, use a button and change it with appropriate styles. Learn more: https://github.com/evcohen/eslint-plugin-jsx-a11y/blob/master/docs/rules/anchor-is-valid.md","JSXOpeningElement","jsx-a11y/alt-text","img elements must have an alt prop, either with meaningful text, or an empty string for decorative images.","React Hook useEffect has a missing dependency: 'form'. Either include it or remove the dependency array.",["556"],["557"],"eqeqeq","Expected '===' and instead saw '=='.","BinaryExpression","unexpected","React Hook useEffect has a missing dependency: 'setUser'. Either include it or remove the dependency array. If 'setUser' changes too often, find the parent component that defines it and wrap that definition in useCallback.",["558"],"React Hook useEffect has missing dependencies: 'history', 'idProduct', 'socket', and 'token'. Either include them or remove the dependency array.",["559"],["560"],["561"],["562"],"React Hook useEffect has missing dependencies: 'actionGetCartAPI' and 'token'. Either include them or remove the dependency array.",["563"],"React Hook useEffect has a missing dependency: 'actionGetCart'. Either include it or remove the dependency array.",["564"],["565"],["566"],["567"],"no-mixed-operators","Unexpected mix of '&&' and '||'.","LogicalExpressi